quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  76,26,"Ne mushilo murerere obweni hasi, ne mutswenule oluwono olurambi lweshilo."
  76,27,"Toto Abandu bano bachama obulamu bwokhushialo, ne balekhanga inyuma wabu inyanga isiro."
  76,28,"Efwe khwabaloonga, ne nikhubaramwo amaani, ne nikhwenya, khunyala okhukalukhasia abandi bali shingabo."
  76,29,"Toto bwene kano ni ametsulisio. Kho, owenya, atiile injila itsia ewa Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  76,30,"Ne shimwakhenya tawe okhula Nyasaye achame. Toto bwene Nyasaye niye Omumanyi muno, Owamachesi po."
  76,31,"Yenjisinjia owayenya mutsimbabasi tsitsie, ne abamabii yabarecheshela eshinyasio eshilulu."
  77,1,"Nditsuba khuchirumungwa kaala!"
  77,2,"Nende chiwutsanga obutinyu."
  77,3,"Nende chimitsanga ifula isalana!"
  77,4,"Nende abamalaika bekhanga okhwaukhasia amalayi nende amabii."
  77,5,"Nende abamalaika bekhanga nende obufimbuli."
  77,6,"Bube khubo eshichila nohomba amekanyilisio."
  77,7,"Toto bwene kamulakungwa kaliba!"
  77,8,"Olwa tsing’ining’ini tsilisumibwa."
  77,9,"Ne olwa likulu liliatisibwa."
  77,10,"Ne olwa efikulu filipurusibwa."
  77,11,"Ne olwa Abarumwa balikhung'asibwa kubise bilala."
  77,12,"Khulwa inyanga shina eyo yasutibwa imbeli?"
  77,13,"Khulwa inyanga yokhwaukhania."
  77,14,"Ne shina shikhumanyia inyanga yokhwaukhania?"
  77,15,"Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakatsulanga."
  77,16,"Shikhwasishia abaranjilila?"
  77,17,"Mana nikhubalondiakhwo abeinyuma?"
  77,18,"Endio nilwakhukholanga Abandu ababii."
  77,19,"Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubakhayi."